Hornick says guests can see downtown Tampa and even St. Petersburg, some 30 miles away from the top of the ride.

Once riders get to the top of the tower, a computer program determines how long it stays at the peak before the gut-wrenching plunge. 

Hornick said the wait time at the top will be randomised, anywhere from one to five seconds.

During the drop, riders will experience an estimated G-force of 3.5gs.

